        "content": "<h2>Pacifica</h2><p><em>[ Pa`ci´fi`ca]</em> means peaceful.</p><p>Recalls the natural beauty of the pacific coastline.</p><p>Inspired by a lyric by Joao and Astrud Gilberto, a song that played during Pacifica's envisioning.</p>",
