            "image": "shopify://shop_images/about_us_mockup_beyond_clean.png",
            "tab_label": "",
            "subheading": "",
            "title": "beyond clean",
            "content": "<p>We believe that what we put on our skin is as important as what we put in our bodies and into the environment. </p><p>Built to defy the industry’s notion that beauty cannot be both clean and effective, Pacifica Beauty proves that nature and science can coalesce in our high performance, 100% vegan<strong> </strong>and<strong> </strong>cruelty-free formulas<strong> </strong>made with intentional ingredients for real results. </p><p>We abide by our strict Compassion Standards™, which include over 1,800 ingredients we will never use. </p>",
            "button_text": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
      },
