            "content": "<p>We use PCR (post-consumer recycled plastic), glass, and/or aluminum, and our outer cartons are made from sustainably sourced paper certified by the Forest Stewardship Council™. </p><p>In partnership with Plastic Collective™, Pacifica Beauty provides funds to help support the development of plastic recycling social enterprises and address plastic waste in territories with high environmental leakage. </p>",
